    Title: The All-Wise Doorkeeper
Tags:
  - Union-Identity=Mysterium Magnum=Silence
  - Discernment-Truth=Reality=The One and the Many
  - Creation=Simultaneity of the Divine Act
Commentary: |
  This is equatable with the Sat-Chit-Ananda of Hinduism.
---
God is an Eternal Being, an Infinite Unity, the Radical Principle of all
things. His Essence is Infinite Light. His Power -- Omnipotence; His Will --
Perfect Goodness; His Wish -- Absolute Reality. As we strive to think of Him,
we plunge into the Abyss of Silence, of infinite Glory.
